duck: English Language Development - ELT is a widely-used teacher-centred term, as in the English language teaching divisions of large publishing houses, ELT training, etc.
Electroluminescent display - Electroluminescent Displays are a type of Flat panel display created by sandwiching a layer of electroluminescent material such as GaAs between two layers of conductors.
Old age or eld, the advancement of years
Extraordinary low dispersion glass - Low dispersion glass (LD glass) is a type of glass with low dispersion.
